    "sections": {
        "description": "<p>Cheritto&#8217;s Admin Posts Grid let you view the posts table as a grid of cards.</p>\n<ul>\n<li>several themes available;</li>\n<li>hide or show image, title, author, tags, categories and post date inside cards;</li>\n<li>adjustable number of columns;</li>\n<li>per-user preferences;</li>\n<li>quick edit support via ajax modal form.</li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Issues</h3>\n<p>If you find issues using this plugin please send feedback, I&#8217;ll do my best to fix asap.</p>\n",
        "installation": "<p>Just activate the plugin, you&#8217;ll find a new admin menu page on the left: &#8220;Posts grid&#8221;. Enjoy!</p>\n",
        "changelog": "<h4>1.0.5</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix style of lock when a different user is editing the post.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.4</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix inline edit</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.3</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix bulk actions</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.2</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Fix tag links</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.1</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>Small fix in css loading.</li>\n</ul>\n<h4>1.0.0</h4>\n<ul>\n<li>First release.</li>\n</ul>\n"
    },
